[SN]TITLE[SN]
Bell-ringer saved by Derbyshire mountain rescue team

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An elderly bell-ringer had to be removed from a Derbyshire church by a mountain rescue team after becoming tangled in bell ropes.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
19 January 2015 Last updated at 19:49 GMT
The team was called to free the unnamed victim from a church tower at Brailsford's All Saints Church after she injured her hip, as Amy Harris reports.
